---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Cai" noIndex={true}>
  <Navbar />
  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>1. Data Protection at a Glance</h2>
        <h3>General Information</h3>
        <p>
          The following information provides a simple overview of what happens to your personal data when you use Cai.
          Personal data is any data that can be used to identify you personally.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>2. Privacy-First Philosophy</h2>
        <p>
          Cai is built with privacy as a core principle. All AI processing happens locally on your machine. Your clipboard
          data and text selections never leave your computer. We do not collect, transmit, or store any of your personal
          content or clipboard data.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>3. Data Collection on Our Website</h2>

        <h3>Privacy-Friendly Analytics</h3>
        <p>
          We use <a href="https://www.goatcounter.com/help/privacy" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GoatCounter</a> and <a href="https://umami.is/privacy" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Umami</a>, both privacy-friendly web analytics tools, to understand basic website usage. These tools:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Do not use cookies or track personal information</li>
          <li>Do not track users across websites</li>
          <li>Do not store IP addresses</li>
          <li>Collect only anonymous aggregate statistics (page views, referrers, browser types)</li>
          <li>Are fully GDPR compliant without requiring cookie consent</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Server Log Files</h3>
        <p>
          The website provider automatically collects and stores information in server log files that your browser
          automatically transmits. These include:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Operating system used</li>
          <li>Referrer URL</li>
          <li>Time of the server request</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          This data is not merged with other data sources and is used solely for technical operation and security purposes.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>4. Local Data Processing</h2>
        <p>
          When you use Cai, all text processing occurs on your device through your locally installed AI platform
          (LM Studio, Ollama, etc.). Cai does not collect, transmit, or store any of your data on our servers.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you connect Cai to a cloud AI provider (such as OpenAI or Gemini), your selected text is sent to that
          service for processing. This is entirely opt-in — by default, Cai uses a local built-in model. API keys
          are stored locally on your Mac and are never transmitted to Cai.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>5. Crash Reporting (Optional)</h2>
        <p>
          Cai includes optional, anonymous crash reporting via Sentry. This is disabled by default and only enabled
          if you opt in. When enabled, crash reports contain technical diagnostic data (error type, stack traces,
          OS version) and never include clipboard content, AI conversations, or personal information. You can disable
          crash reporting at any time in Cai's settings.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          This website is hosted on GitHub Pages. Please refer to
          <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-privacy-statement" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub's Privacy Statement</a>
          for information about their data processing practices.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          You have the right to information about your stored personal data, its origin and recipients, and the purpose
          of data processing at any time free of charge. You also have the right to request the correction or deletion
          of this data. For this purpose and for further questions on the subject of data protection, you can contact
          us at any time.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>8. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about data protection, please contact us at:<br />
          Email: <span id="email-address"></span>
        </p>
      </section>

      <script>
        const user = "web";
        const domain = "getcai.app";
        const element = document.getElementById("email-address");
        if (element) {
          element.innerHTML = `<a href="mailto:${user}@${domain}" class="link">${user}@${domain}</a>`;
        }
      </script>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: February 2026</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0A0A0A 0%, #111111 100%);
    padding: 10rem 0 6rem;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gradient-start) 0%, var(--gradient-end) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .legal-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .legal-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .legal-section h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #E0E0E0;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .legal-section p {
    color: #B0B0B0;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .legal-section ul {
    color: #B0B0B0;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-left: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .legal-section li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .link {
    color: var(--accent-light);
    text-decoration: underline;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .link:hover {
    color: var(--accent-pink);
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: #808080;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-page {
      padding: 7rem 0 4rem;
    }

    .page-title {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .legal-section {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .legal-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .legal-section h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .legal-section p,
    .legal-section ul {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
